    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Extinct genus of horses. Fossils of Merychippus are found at many late Miocene localities throughout the United States, dating from from 17-11 million years ago.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
